{
  "stem": "12684.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of them were Jewish, some of them were not.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it didn't make any difference.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I still know a lady, or girl, or whatever you want to call it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went to school with her at Milburg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we are still friendly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Whenever I go to Europe, I see her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it started in [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] '32, you know, before Hitler came to power.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they had already the inkling that Jews were not the best people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so, sometimes, people would make remarks in a store or whatever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like, oh, the little Jewish girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that's not all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Until '33, of course, things changed rapidly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People took a stand, whether they just took a stand as to not be punished by others, or what, but there were people who didn't want to have anything to do with us anymore.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And people who [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] were especially nice, which is very difficult for a child to understand.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother had an awful lot of explaining to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother remarried the day when we were transplanted to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She married then Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Rudolphi, who was a judge, but he got pensioned off very early.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he did an awful lot of work for the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] since he had a daughter from a former marriage who was half Jewish, he had not been in any danger that he needed to be transported or deported, which, of course, the minute when he married my mother, that was alleviated.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they married one day before we came to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I only know that-- for once-- once, she said to me, always be proud of what you are and a leopard doesn't change its spots, so neither can you.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
